title: Boys cross country rankings for Oct. 5, 2015
text:
By Brad Wilson | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 05, 2015 5:44 PM View/Post Comments 
This week, the results confirmed the rankings for boys cross country at lehighvalleylive.com. 
Voorheesâ€™ absolute dominance of its race at the Shore Coaches Invitational confirmed its No. 1 spot. The team order of finish at the Paul Short Run at Lehigh of the four top EPC followed the rankings as well. 
But Southern Lehigh handled Notre Dame in a dual meet, and that shakes up the lower five of the rankings.
